  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Postoperative sore throat is a complication after general anesthesia requiring endotracheal
      intubation. The investigators will evaluate the efficacy of lidocaine jelly application on
      the endotracheal tube with taper-shaped cuff regarding postoperative sore throat.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
